              <p>Have a look around, see what projects I've worked on, what I've got coming up, and learn a bit more about me. <br><br>
                I'm open to a web development role in London or remote. If you see something that interests you, please get in touch  â†— <br>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="projects-tab tab" id="delay2">
          <h2 class="tab-heading">Projects</h2>
          <div class="tab-surround">
            <div class="hide-div" style="background-image: url()">
              <%= render 'projects' %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-me-tab tab" id="delay3">
          <h2 class="tab-heading">About</h2>
          <div class="tab-surround">
            <div class="hide-div" style="background-image: url()">
              <%= render 'about' %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

